        <h2 id="what-is-proprofs" class="scroll-mt-20">What is ProProfs Chat?</h2>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat is a comprehensive live chat software solution designed to help businesses engage with their website visitors in real-time. As part of the broader ProProfs suite of business tools, it focuses on providing reliable, feature-rich live chat functionality that enables companies to offer instant customer support, generate leads, and improve overall customer experience.</p>

        <p>Unlike AI-powered chatbots that provide automated responses, ProProfs Chat is built around human-to-human interaction, connecting your website visitors directly with your support team or sales representatives. This approach ensures personalized, contextual conversations that can address complex customer needs and build stronger relationships.</p>
        
        <p>Visit <a href="https://www.proprofs.com/chat/" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline">ProProfs Chat official website</a> to explore all features and get started with their platform.</p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 border border-blue-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🎯 Who Uses ProProfs Chat?</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🏢</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Enterprises</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Large organizations with dedicated support teams</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🛒</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">E-commerce</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Online stores needing sales and support assistance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💼</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Service Businesses</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Companies prioritizing customer service excellence</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="core-features" class="scroll-mt-20">Core Features and Capabilities</h2>

        <h3>🏢 ProProfs Chat Plans and Tiers</h3>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat offers multiple plan tiers designed to accommodate businesses of different sizes and needs:</p>
        
