          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Available Plan Tiers</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h5 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3">🚀 Starter Plans</h5>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• Basic live chat functionality</li>
                <li>• Essential customization options</li>
                <li>• Standard reporting features</li>
                <li>• Email support included</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h5 class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-3">🏢 Business & Enterprise</h5>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• Advanced chat routing and automation</li>
                <li>• Comprehensive analytics and reporting</li>
                <li>• Multiple integrations and APIs</li>
                <li>• Priority support and training</li>
                <li>• White-label options available</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">All plans include core live chat features with varying levels of customization and support.</p>
            <a href="https://www.proprofs.com/chat/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium">
              View Current Plans & Pricing
              <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3>🚀 Live Chat Functionality</h3>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat excels in providing robust real-time communication features:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Real-time Messaging:</strong> Instant communication between visitors and support agents with typing indicators and read receipts</li>
          <li><strong>Smart Chat Routing:</strong> Automatic distribution of incoming chats to available agents based on skills, departments, or availability</li>
          <li><strong>Canned Responses:</strong> Pre-written responses for frequently asked questions to speed up response times</li>
          <li><strong>File Sharing:</strong> Share documents, images, screenshots, and files during conversations</li>
          <li><strong>Chat Transcripts:</strong> Complete conversation history with searchable archives</li>
          <li><strong>Visitor Information:</strong> Real-time visitor details including location, browsing history, and referral source</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-chat Management:</strong> Agents can handle multiple conversations simultaneously</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>🎨 Customization and Branding</h3>
        
        <p>The platform offers extensive customization options to match your brand:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Chat Widget Design:</strong> Customize colors, fonts, position, and overall appearance</li>
          <li><strong>Branding Elements:</strong> Add your company logo, brand colors, and custom styling</li>
          <li><strong>Welcome Messages:</strong> Create personalized greetings for different pages or visitor segments</li>
          <li><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> Set availability schedules and automatic responses for offline periods</li>
          <li><strong>Offline Forms:</strong> Capture visitor information and messages when agents are unavailable</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Fields:</strong> Collect specific information from visitors before starting chats</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>📊 Analytics and Reporting</h3>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat provides comprehensive analytics to help you understand and improve your customer service performance:</p>
        
