          <li><strong>Chat Volume Reports:</strong> Track conversation trends, peak hours, and seasonal patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Agent Performance Metrics:</strong> Monitor response times, chat duration, and customer satisfaction scores</li>
          <li><strong>Visitor Analytics:</strong> Understand visitor behavior, popular pages, and engagement patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Conversion Tracking:</strong> Measure how live chat impacts sales, leads, and business goals</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Dashboards:</strong> Create personalized reports focusing on metrics that matter to your business</li>
          <li><strong>Real-time Monitoring:</strong> Live view of ongoing chats and agent activity</li>
        </ul>

