        <h2 id="user-experience" class="scroll-mt-20">User Experience and Interface Design</h2>

        <h3>👥 Agent Dashboard</h3>
        
        <p>The agent interface is designed for efficiency and ease of use:</p>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Key Dashboard Features:</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Clean, intuitive layout with easy navigation</li>
              <li>• Multi-chat management with tabbed interface</li>
              <li>• Visitor queue showing waiting customers</li>
              <li>• Quick access to canned responses and files</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Real-time notifications and alerts</li>
              <li>• Agent status controls (available, busy, away)</li>
              <li>• Chat history and transcript search</li>
              <li>• Performance metrics and statistics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3>🌟 Visitor Experience</h3>
        
        <p>From the customer's perspective, ProProfs Chat delivers a smooth, professional experience:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Fast Loading:</strong> Lightweight chat widget that doesn't impact website performance</li>
          <li><strong>Intuitive Interface:</strong> Simple, clean design that's easy for anyone to use</li>
          <li><strong>Proactive Engagement:</strong> Smart triggers to initiate conversations at the right moment</li>
          <li><strong>File Upload:</strong> Easy sharing of screenshots, documents, and other files</li>
          <li><strong>Chat History:</strong> Visitors can review previous conversations</li>
          <li><strong>Satisfaction Surveys:</strong> Post-chat feedback collection</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="implementation" class="scroll-mt-20">Implementation and Setup Process</h2>

        <h3>🚀 Getting Started</h3>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat is designed for quick and easy implementation:</p>
        
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Account Setup:</strong> Create your ProProfs Chat account and configure basic settings</li>
          <li><strong>Widget Customization:</strong> Design your chat widget to match your brand</li>
          <li><strong>Website Integration:</strong> Add the chat code to your website (simple copy-paste process)</li>
          <li><strong>Agent Training:</strong> Set up agent accounts and provide training on the platform</li>
