          <ul class="text-green-800 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Start with a soft launch to a limited audience</li>
            <li>• Create comprehensive canned responses for common questions</li>
            <li>• Set up proper chat routing based on your team structure</li>
            <li>• Configure operating hours to match your support availability</li>
            <li>• Train agents on best practices for live chat communication</li>
          </ul>
